research_municipality_step.notes: Murphy, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Mayor and Council Members for Places 1, 2, 4, and 6 are based on the unofficial results of the May 3, 2025, general election. The Mayor Pro Tem role for Elizabeth Abraham is also noted. For Council Members in Places 3 and 5, the most recent specific names available are from a 2020 list, and their continued tenure is assumed in the absence of more recent election results for those specific places.
